data.description: **This home is available for lease purchase** Incredible opportunity to own this expansive 5 bedroom, 3 bath home with OWNED solar panels! Situated on a great lot in the Casa Grande community of Villago, this home is just steps away from a huge park, playground and basketball court! Inside you will find a large formal living/dining area, which leads into a spacious great room that is open to the kitchen and dining space.  The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, granite counters, an island with a breakfast bar and walk in pantry. A full-sized bathroom and bedroom are conveniently located downstairs perfect for guests.  Upstairs you will find a huge loft and 4 additional bedrooms including a master bedroom with an attached bathroom and walk in closet! The 3rd tandem garage has been converted into a fully functional room with heat and air conditioning, and a private entrance! This space has endless possibilities including a home gym, workshop, additional bedroom, etc. In addition, the garage has newer mechanics and computer installed last year, and a new 4-ton AC unit was installed in March of 2023 for the downstairs. Finally, the backyard is ready for you to make it your own and is equipped with an RV gate, a sunken fire pit space as well as two extended paver pads perfect for a hot tub, grill or gazebo! With over 3,000 square feet this home has something for everyone!
